tursodatabase/limbo.summary: Recent activities on the tursodatabase/limbo repository include three pull request events. The first event, simulator: allow failure assertions, adds creating the same table twice to the list of checked properties as a failure property example. The second event, Fix submission queue overflow on large blob writes, addresses an issue with submission queue overflow by increasing the sub queue entries size. The third event, Fixes like function giving incorrect results when pattern has regex meta chars, resolves an issue where the like function was giving incorrect results when the pattern contained regex meta characters by properly escaping the required characters.
